channel.title: Youtube - Accidental Deletion.
channel.description:
I've accidentally deleted a video off of my YouTube account, and it was from a few years ago, so it's not on my PC, is there anyway that I can recover it from YouTube?
Any help would be appreciated, thanks. ^_^
